---
layout: base.njk
pagination:
  data: cities
  size: 1
  alias: city
permalink: "/commercial-real-estate/{{ city.state_abbr }}/{{ city.slug }}/index.html"
title: "Commercial Real Estate in {{ city.city }}, {{ city.state_abbr }}"
description: "{% if city.meta_description %}{{ city.meta_description }}{% elseif city.tier == 1 %}Explore commercial real estate in {{ city.city }}, {{ city.state_abbr }}, one of the most active business markets in the state. Browse office, retail, and industrial space and discover opportunities across the market.{% elseif city.county %}Explore commercial real estate in {{ city.city }}, {{ city.state_abbr }}, located in {{ city.county }}. Browse office, retail, and industrial properties and discover nearby opportunities with Rofo.{% else %}Explore commercial real estate in {{ city.city }}, {{ city.state_abbr }}. Browse office, retail, and industrial properties and discover nearby opportunities with Rofo.{% endif %}"
---

<style>
  .city-page {
    padding: 32px 0 56px;
  }

  .city-page .city-shell {
    max-width: 1180px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .city-page .city-hero {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.35fr) minmax(320px, 0.95fr);
    gap: 24px;
    align-items: stretch;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .city-page .city-card,
  .city-page .city-sidecard,
  .city-page .city-stat,
  .city-page .city-form {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #d8e0ea;
    border-radius: 18px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
  }

  .city-page .city-card,
  .city-page .city-sidecard,
  .city-page .city-form {
    padding: 24px;
  }

  .city-page .eyebrow {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: .08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #556274;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .city-page h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
    line-height: 1.08;
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    color: #0f172a;
  }

  .city-page h2 {
    font-size: 1.55rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    color: #0f172a;
  }

  .city-page h3 {
    font-size: 1.08rem;
    line-height: 1.25;
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    color: #0f172a;
  }

  .city-page p {
    color: #334155;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin: 0 0 14px;
  }

  .city-page .lead {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: #475569;
    max-width: 62ch;
  }

  .city-page .pill-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 16px;
  }

  .city-page .pill {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #f1f5f9;
    color: #0f172a;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .city-page .hero-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    min-height: 320px;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    border-radius: 14px;
  }

  .city-page .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .city-page .city-stat {
    padding: 18px;
  }

  .city-page .stat-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: .08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #64748b;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .city-page .stat-value {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0f172a;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .city-page .stat-note {
    color: #64748b;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .city-page .city-main {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.9fr) minmax(280px, 0.95fr);
    gap: 24px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .city-page .stack {
    display: grid;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .city-page .building-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .city-page .building-card {
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 18px;
    background: #fbfdff;
  }

  .city-page .building-meta {
    color: #64748b;
    font-size: 0.94rem;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .city-page .building-link,
  .city-page .market-links a,
  .city-page .back-link {
    color: #1346d8;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .city-page .building-link:hover,
  .city-page .market-links a:hover,
  .city-page .back-link:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .city-page .market-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px 12px;
  }

  .city-page .market-links a {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 9px 12px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #f8fafc;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    font-size: 0.93rem;
  }

  .city-page .city-form label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #334155;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .city-page .city-form input,
  .city-page .city-form textarea {
    width: 100%;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 12px 13px;
    font: inherit;
    color: #0f172a;
    background: #fff;
  }

  .city-page .city-form textarea {
    min-height: 120px;
    resize: vertical;
  }

  .city-page .form-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .city-page .field + .field {
    margin-top: 12px;
  }

  .city-page .form-grid .field + .field {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .city-page .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    border: 0;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 12px 18px;
    font: inherit;
    font-weight: 700;
    background: #1346d8;
    color: #fff;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .city-page .mini-list {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 18px;
    color: #475569;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 980px) {
    .city-page .city-hero,
    .city-page .city-main {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .city-page .stats-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 680px) {
    .city-page .stats-grid,
    .city-page .building-grid,
    .city-page .form-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .city-page .city-shell {
      padding: 0 16px;
    }

    .city-page .city-card,
    .city-page .city-sidecard,
    .city-page .city-stat,
    .city-page .city-form {
      padding: 18px;
    }
  }
</style>

<section class="city-page">
  <div class="city-shell">

    <div class="city-hero">
      <div class="city-card">
        <div class="eyebrow">Market</div>
        <h1>Commercial Real Estate in {{ city.city }}, {{ city.state_abbr }}</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          {{ city.short_description or city.city_description_raw or ("Explore office, retail, and industrial real estate opportunities in " + city.city + ", " + city.state_abbr + ".") }}
        </p>

        <div class="pill-row">
          <span class="pill">Office</span>
          <span class="pill">Retail</span>
          <span class="pill">Industrial</span>
          {% if city.county %}<span class="pill">{{ city.county }}</span>{% endif %}
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="city-sidecard">
        <img
          class="hero-image"
          src="{{ city.hero_image or '/images/cities/city.jpg' }}"
          alt="{{ city.city }}, {{ city.state_abbr }}"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="stats-grid">
      <div class="city-stat">
        <div class="stat-label">Market</div>
        <div class="stat-value">{{ city.city }}</div>
        <p class="stat-note">{{ city.state_abbr }}</p>
      </div>

      <div class="city-stat">
        <div class="stat-label">Buildings</div>
        <div class="stat-value">{{ city.building_count or "—" }}</div>
        <p class="stat-note">Known buildings in this market</p>
      </div>

      <div class="city-stat">
        <div class="stat-label">County</div>
        <div class="stat-value">{{ city.county or "—" }}</div>
        <p class="stat-note">Local market context</p>
      </div>

      <div class="city-stat">
        <div class="stat-label">Coordinates</div>
        <div class="stat-value">{% if city.lat and city.lng %}{{ city.lat }}, {{ city.lng }}{% else %}—{% endif %}</div>
        <p class="stat-note">Reference location</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="city-main">
      <div class="stack">
        <div class="city-card">
          <div class="eyebrow">Overview</div>
          <h2>Explore the {{ city.city }} market</h2>
          <p>
            Rofo helps businesses research commercial real estate in {{ city.city }}, {{ city.state_abbr }}.
            Use this page as a starting point to understand the market, explore representative buildings, and narrow your search.
          </p>
          <p>
            Whether you are looking for office space, retail frontage, or industrial property,
            Rofo is designed to make market discovery simpler and more efficient.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="city-card">
          <div class="eyebrow">Featured Buildings</div>
          <h2>Representative buildings in {{ city.city }}</h2>
          <p>
            This section is currently powered by sample building data and can later be replaced with your real building dataset.
          </p>

          <div class="building-grid">
            {% for building in sampleBuildings %}
              {% if building.city == city.city %}
                <div class="building-card">
                  <h3>{{ building.name }}</h3>
                  <div class="building-meta">{{ building.type }} · {{ building.size }}</div>
                  <p>{{ building.address }}</p>
                  <a class="building-link" href="/commercial-real-estate/{{ building.state_abbr }}/{{ building.city_slug }}/buildings/{{ building.building_slug }}/">
                    View building
                  </a>
                </div>
              {% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="city-card">
          <div class="eyebrow">Nearby Markets</div>
          <h2>Explore nearby cities</h2>
          <p>Browse nearby markets to expand your search.</p>

          <div class="market-links">
            {% if city.nearby_cities and city.nearby_cities.length %}
              {% for nearby in city.nearby_cities %}
                {% set nearbyCity = cityLookup[nearby] %}
                {% if nearbyCity %}
                  <a href="{{ nearbyCity.path }}">{{ nearbyCity.label }}</a>
                {% endif %}
              {% endfor %}
            {% else %}
              <a href="#">Nearby City One</a>
              <a href="#">Nearby City Two</a>
              <a href="#">Nearby City Three</a>
              <a href="#">Nearby City Four</a>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="stack">
        <div class="city-form">
          <div class="eyebrow">Get Help</div>
          <h2>Looking in {{ city.city }}?</h2>
          <p>
            Tell us what you need and we can help point you in the right direction.
          </p>

          <div class="form-grid">
            <div class="field">
              <label>Email</label>
              <input type="email" placeholder="Your email">
            </div>
            <div class="field">
              <label>Market</label>
              <input type="text" value="{{ city.city }}, {{ city.state_abbr }}">
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <label>Property type</label>
            <input type="text" placeholder="Office, retail, industrial...">
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <label>What are you looking for?</label>
            <textarea placeholder="Size, neighborhood, timing, budget, use case, etc."></textarea>
          </div>

          <div style="margin-top: 14px;">
            <button class="btn-primary">Submit</button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="city-card">
          <div class="eyebrow">Why Rofo</div>
          <h2>Start with market context</h2>
          <p>
            Rofo helps businesses discover commercial real estate by market first, then drill into buildings and location options.
          </p>

          <ul class="mini-list">
            <li>Explore markets city by city</li>
            <li>Review representative buildings</li>
            <li>Compare nearby markets</li>
            <li>Get help narrowing your search</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>